latestPosts.caption: Ok… 📢HEAR ME OUT. It’s mid August. It’s 120 degrees outside, and you’re like, “ Hey I don’t really feel like sweating off all my beautiful makeup and burning from the sun” @thatchapeldowntown is probably one of your best options for chapels AND photos WITHOUT having to step foot outside. You can get all the vibey Vegas photos at night downtown too if you want, but I think this is such a nice space for photos and not sweating through your suit. That’s my rant. Have a nice day. #vegasweddingphotographer #lasvegasweddingphotographer #vegaswedding #vegaselopement #vegaselopementphotographer #vegasweddingchapel
